          collection of links to get it running. This site runs on <a href="//11ty.dev">Eleventy</a> and is
          hosted by <a href="//netlify.com">Netlify</a>.
        </p>
        <p>This content is and always be <a href="//github.com/hankchizljaw/educationlinks.fyi">free and open source</a> under the MIT licence.</p>
      </div> 
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
